    "The Bitcoin market is generally more efficient than Ethereum in terms of the length of the efficiency period.",
    "Furthermore, the analysis shows that global financial stress has significant negative effects on the AMIMs of Bitcoin and Ethereum, which concurs with Zhang and Wang (2021), who find that, in comparison to conventional financial markets, crypto markets are relatively insensitive to financial stress.",
    "Furthermore, CC liquidity appears to be a major driver of AMIMs, irrespective of the level of CC (in)efficiency, consistent with previous findings (Wei 2018; Al-Yahyaee et al. 2020).",
    "As documented by Naeem et al. (2021), the impact of the COVID-19 pandemic was positive and significant in both CC markets.",
    "This observation was strengthened because herding behavior was observed, particularly during confined periods."
